A lightweight **Flask-based academic management system** for handling users, programs, semesters, questions, and evaluation workflows.

The project is fully containerized and includes **Docker Compose for local development** and **Kubernetes manifests for production deployment**.

---

## ğŸ“Œ Features

- User & academic data management
- MySQL relational database
- Jinja2 server-side rendering
- Dockerized development environment
- Kubernetes deployment manifests
- Production-ready with Gunicorn

